  "page": "Mother (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <a href=\"/index.php/Mother\" title=\"Mother\">Mother</a> is the leader of a motherhouse.\n</p><p>Mother can also refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Maiden,_Mother,_and_Crone\" title=\"Maiden, Mother, and Crone\">Maiden, Mother, and Crone</a>, a song.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Mother\" title=\"Moon Mother\">Moon Mother</a>, a deity in Essos.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">Mother</a>, one of the aspects of the deity worshipped by the Faith of the Seven.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother%27s_(brothel)\" title=\"Mother&#39;s (brothel)\">Mother's</a>, a brothel in the Street of Silk in King's Landing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother%27s_Men\" title=\"Mother&#39;s Men\">Mother's Men</a>, a company of fighting men.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Mother Merciless</a>, an alias of Lady Stoneheart.</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Mother%27s_Mercy\" title=\"Mother&#39;s Mercy\">Mother's Mercy</a></i>, an episode of the TV-show <i>Game of Thrones</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother_Mole\" title=\"Mother Mole\">Mother Mole</a>, a wildling leader.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother_Rhoyne\" title=\"Mother Rhoyne\">Mother Rhoyne</a>, the chief goddess of the Rhoynar.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mother%27s_Tears\" title=\"The Mother&#39;s Tears\">The Mother's Tears</a>, a song.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother%27s_Teats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mother&#39;s Teats\">Mother's Teats</a>, a pair of grassy hills in the riverlands.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother_of_Dragons\" title=\"Mother of Dragons\">Mother of Dragons</a>, an honorific title assumed by Daenerys Targaryen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother_of_Mountains\" title=\"Mother of Mountains\">Mother of Mountains</a>, a mountain that lies within sight of Vaes Dothrak.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mother-of-pearl\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mother-of-pearl\">Mother-of-pearl</a>, a type of gemstone.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Mother\" title=\"Old Mother\">Old Mother</a>, a pirate queen.</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Mother%27s_Son\" title=\"Old Mother&#39;s Son\">Old Mother's Son</a></i>, a galley in the fleet of Salladhor Saan.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404235412\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:30885-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404235412 and revision id 285435\n -->\n",
